title: Street closed for water main repair
title_page: Street closed for water main repair
maintext:
NORFOLK - Due to water main repair, Michigan Avenue from Thirteenth Street to Glen Street will be closed from 6:00 a.m. until approximately 2:00 p.m. Tuesday.
If you have questions regarding this closure please contact the Water and Sewer Division at 402-844-2210.
